<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1065139-would-this-series-be-good-for-an-agatha">Would this series be good for an Agatha Christie fan?!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1065139'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F498594.Death_by_Darjeeling">like</a></span>

