        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2546102676" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16415948073734883379">There are many cozy mysteries set in tea shops, but this one has something more: the tea shop is not merely a cozy setting, the reader also gets to know the culture of tea drinking and brewing. It&apos;s a very interesting book in that respect. My only complaint is that the ending felt pretty rushed, other than that I really enjoyed this novel and will definitely go on reading the other books in the series.</span>
  <span id="freeText16415948073734883379" style="display:none">There are many cozy mysteries set in tea shops, but this one has something more: the tea shop is not merely a cozy setting, the reader also gets to know the culture of tea drinking and brewing. It's a very interesting book in that respect. My only complaint is that the ending felt pretty rushed, other than that I really enjoyed this novel and will definitely go on reading the other books in the series.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16415948073734883379" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

