<div id="review_3670085263" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3670085263" />
    <a title="Sarah" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/33969072-sarah"><img alt="Sarah" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1408051069p2/33969072.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3670085263?book_show_action=true">Dec 07, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sarah" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sarah" href="/user/show/33969072-sarah">Sarah</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/8134197-death-by-darjeeling">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/33969072-sarah?shelf=2020">2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/33969072-sarah?shelf=mystery-thriller">mystery-thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/33969072-sarah?shelf=cozy-mystery">cozy-mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/33969072-sarah?shelf=published-2000-to-2009">published-2000-to-2009</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/33969072-sarah?shelf=tbr-cozy-mystery">tbr-cozy-mystery</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3670085263" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9169321854120709595">Kinda cheesy at certain points, kinda dated, and there wasn&apos;t really a lot of active solving as far as the mystery went. And yet, this hit the spot as far as the coziness I was looking for. Really liked the cast of characters, the small town feel (even in what is a good-sized city), and the descriptions of tea. Will definitely read more in this series when the urge hits me to curl up with a comforting read and a cup of tea.</span>
  <span id="freeText9169321854120709595" style="display:none">Kinda cheesy at certain points, kinda dated, and there wasn't really a lot of active solving as far as the mystery went. And yet, this hit the spot as far as the coziness I was looking for. Really liked the cast of characters, the small town feel (even in what is a good-sized city), and the descriptions of tea. Will definitely read more in this series when the urge hits me to curl up with a comforting read and a cup of tea.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9169321854120709595" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
